      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2021-06-17</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2021-12-02T22:01:41Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Municipal IDs Acceptance Act </strong></p> <p>This bill directs financial regulatory agencies to update specified guidance to include municipal identification cards as acceptable forms of identification for purposes of verifying the identity of a bank customer. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
